The saying "you're never too old to learn" emphasizes the importance of continuous learning. Now it's time to put that concept into elegant Chinese words. Join CGTN's Niuniu and learn about a poem that compares book reading to a glassy oblong pool. This video series provides you with inspirational ancient wisdom that still applies today. We learn about significant figures in Chinese history through tours of their hometowns, bring their life stories back to life and learn the reasons behind Xi Jinping citing their sayings so that we could have better insights on Xi's Chinese wisdom and global view.